consists on Nodes in a parent, child relationship
lists are linear
trees are non-linear
singly linked list can be a special path for tree
nodes only can refrence nodes that below them
you need to have one entry point 
vocabs:   1- root: the top node in a tree
         2- child:  a node connecting to another node when moving                    away from the Root.
         3-  parent: the converse notion of a child
         4- leaf: a node with no children 
         5- edge:  the connection between two nodes(the arrow)           